title: match history bug

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: it shows mundo had the highest killing spree of four when thresh clearly had a killing spree of 5

replies.body:
That's a bug in how long of a killing spree thresh has then.

Thersh kills lucian, then Riven kills thresh, so he can't have a 5 killing spree.

EDIT: In fact looking over the whole thing, he has a killing spree of 1.
but thresh obviously doesn't have a five kill spree bro lol
